title: VIDEO: Aziz Ansari's New Netflix Series Looks Pretty Promising
text: VIDEO: Aziz Ansari's New Netflix Series Looks Pretty Promising Thursday, 22 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) The trailer for Ansari's new Netflix series, Master of None, introduces us to Dev (Ansari), a 30-year-old struggling actor dealing with everyday issues including relationships, racism and life in general. [...] it's clear the new comedy is geared more towards Netflix than traditional broadcast - the two-minute clip features the F-bomb and a frank discussion between Dev and his girlfriend Rachel (Saturday Night Live's Noel Wells) about whether they should get the morning-after pill when the condom they're using breaks.
